Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.yokogawa.Yokogawa6370, [':FORMat:DATA REAL,64',
    ':TRAC:ACTIVE TRA', ':TRAC:ACTIVE TRD', ':TRAC:ACTIVE?',
    ':TRAC:ACTIVE?'], ['TRB', 'TRG']) as inst:
    inst.active_trace = inst.Traces.A
    inst.active_trace = inst.Traces.D
    assert inst.active_trace == inst.Traces.B
    assert inst.active_trace == inst.Traces.G
